FT  07 MAY 92 / UK Company News: Aspen buys Dutch market consultancy
Aspen Communications, the specialist print, communications and media
services group, is acquiring Veenhuizen Reclame, a direct market consultancy
in the Netherlands.
The initial consideration is Pounds 760,000 cash, payable to Cumae Beheer,
the vendor. Depending on profits performance, there could be further
payments up to a maximum of Pounds 365,000.
